OL,6,FA wheelchair user has praised the
OL,7,Faccessibility of the National
OL,8,FEisteddfod 2024 but calls for more to
OL,9,Fbe done in future.
OL,11,FEmily Nicole Roberts, 26, lives with
OL,12,Fcerebral palsy, is calling for more
OL,13,Fstewards to help, more signs on the
OL,14,FMaes, and less pathways made of gravel
OL,15,Fat the event in future.
OL,17,FWith the field in Ynys Angharad Park
OL,18,Fin Pontypridd, the National Eisteddfod
OL,19,Ffestival site looks a bit different
OL,20,Fthan usual his year.
