OL,6,FEmily, who works in a bridal shop,
OL,7,Falso has her own Youtube series 'How
OL,8,FEmily.' Her series will be adapted to
OL,9,Fa show on BBC Radio Wales after a
OL,10,Fsuccessful pilot last year.
OL,12,FIn the series, Emily shows how she
OL,13,Fcompletes tasks and takes part in
OL,14,Factivities as a wheelchair user.
OL,16,FThis week, she shared her experience
OL,17,Fin the Eisteddfod with the 'Hansh Dim
OL,18,FSbin' team.
OL,20,FSo, just how accessible was the event
OL,21,Ffor a wheelchair user?
