OL,6,FA good start on arrival
OL,8,FBefore arriving, Emily said the
OL,9,FEisteddfod's website was "full of
OL,10,Finformation about accessibility,
OL,11,Fbetter than i've seen before".
OL,13,FEmily and her family parked in the
OL,14,Fblue badge parking area, around 10
OL,15,Fminutes away from Ynysangharad Park,
OL,16,Fto try and avoid potential
OL,17,Funreliability of public transport.
