OL,3,CWheelchair user praises Eisteddfod
OL,4,Caccessibility but wants more to be done
OL,6,FArriving at the festival, Emily was
OL,7,Fhappy to see that most of the paths
OL,8,Fthrough the field were flat, but she
OL,9,Fwas "scared of the grass" in case she
OL,10,Fgot stuck.
OL,12,FThe learners' field (Maes D)
OL,14,FEmily is a Welsh learner so had been
OL,15,Flooking forward to visiting Maes D,
OL,16,Fbut the biggest problem she faced on
OL,17,Fthe field was getting to their tent.
OL,19,FThe path which leads down to Maes D is
OL,20,Fsteep and quite uneven.
