OL,4,Caccessibility but wants more to be done
OL,6,FWith no other accessible option, Emily
OL,7,Ftried to use the path to get down to
OL,8,Fthe tent but she got stuck.
OL,10,FKnowing she would not be able to go
OL,11,Fback up the hill to the main pavement
OL,12,Fof the field, she had to accept the
OL,13,Fhelp of someone passing by to pull her
OL,14,Fup.
OL,16,FWhen visiting the stalls Emily found
OL,17,Fit difficult to get in and out of them.
OL,19,FBecause of the space between the path
OL,20,Fand the grass, and then a steep ramp,
OL,21,Fshe needed help to get in and out.
