OL,6,F"The ramps (into the stalls) are steep
OL,7,Fso you need to have strong arms, which
OL,8,FI don't have," she said.
OL,10,FTo get out and get back on the
OL,11,Fpavement, she needed help getting her
OL,12,Fwheelchair back up as well.
OL,14,FIn other areas of the field, there
OL,15,Fwere some steep areas which meant she
OL,16,Fhad to get help once again.
