OL,6,FIn the field facing the main stage,
OL,7,Fthere are benches which leave room for
OL,8,Fwheelchair users.
OL,10,FEmily said benches like this made her
OL,11,Ffeel like part of a group, instead of
OL,12,Fsitting at the head of the table.
OL,14,F"I love them," she said.
OL,16,FGoing over the lawn with the
OL,17,Fwheelchair, Emily said: "The grass is
OL,18,Ffine now, but when it rains that's a
OL,19,Fbig problem."
