OL,6,FOverall, Emily was satisfied that the
OL,7,Ffloor of the field was level and that
OL,8,Fshe could access a wheelchair site in
OL,9,Fthe Pavilion, and accessible toilets
OL,10,Fnear the Lido.
OL,12,FHer intention is to use social media
OL,13,Fto raise awareness of the challenges
OL,14,Fand stereotypes which disabled people
OL,15,Fface.
OL,17,FA spokesperson for the Eisteddfod
OL,18,Fsaid: "We brief all our stewards
OL,19,Fduring their training, and Ollie, our
OL,20,Faccessibility officer, is part of the
OL,21,Fbriefing before the Eisteddfod starts.
